{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"title":"Fruit Filling","content":["Place orange peelings and vanilla sugar in mixing bowl then grind <nobr>10 sec\/speed 10<\/nobr>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula.","Add apples, pears, cinnamon stick, cloves and star anise then cook <nobr>10 min\/100°C\/\/speed <\/nobr>. Meanwhile, grease a rectangular baking dish (approx. 26 cm x 24 cm x 5 cm). Transfer contents of mixing bowl to prepared dish then scatter blackberries over surface. Clean mixing bowl and make topping."]},{"title":"Topping","content":["Preheat oven to 170°C. Place ginger in mixing bowl and chop <nobr>3 sec\/speed 7<\/nobr>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula.","Add flour, sugar, baking powder, bicarbonate of soda and salt then mix <nobr>15 sec\/speed 3<\/nobr>.","Add butter and mix <nobr>5 sec\/speed 7<\/nobr>.","Add buttermilk and mix <nobr>10 sec\/speed 3<\/nobr>. Tip out onto a generously floured work surface and flatten to 1.5 cm thick. Using a cookie cutter (5 cm), cut out preferred shapes of dough and place on fruit, with approx. 5 cm between each. Re-roll any trimmings to cut further shapes.","Brush shapes lightly with buttermilk then sprinkle with Demerara sugar. Bake for 35-45 minutes (170°C) until cobbler topping is cooked and well browned.","Serve hot - delicious with cream, custard or ice cream."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"Fruit Filling","content":["½ orange, thin peelings of skin","100 g vanilla sugar","400 g cooking apples (e.g. Bramley) peeled, cored, cut in pieces (2 cm)","400 g pears, peeled, cored, cut in pieces (4 cm)","1 cinnamon stick","2 cloves","2 star anise","200 g blackberries"]},{"title":"Topping","content":["80 g unsalted butter, diced, plus extra for greasing","35 g crystallised ginger, diced","170 g plain flour, plus extra for dusting","75 g granulated sugar","¾ tsp baking powder","½ tsp bicarbonate of soda","½ tsp coarse salt","60 g buttermilk, plus extra for brushing","1 Tbsp Demerara sugar, for sprinkling"]}],"id":"r133219","imageLink":"https:\/\/1.bp.blogspot.com\/-snshj14J8zw\/XZWcfGalZPI\/AAAAAAAAeaU\/1dSCqD1P6PsXrsyih81yYjn_A840upIbgCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_0-eEwhf6aNEl7M2I.png","title":"Spiced Autumn Fruit Cobbler","publishedAt":"2017-11-24T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"3.1 g","fat":"8.7 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"56 g","calories":"1316 kJ \/ 315 kcal"},"usefulItems":"rectangular baking dish (26 cm x 24 cm x 5 cm), cookie cutter, rolling pin, pastry brush, oven","basicInfo":["easy","20m","1h 20m","8 portions"]}